title: Nottingham shopper films cat looking out from rucksack
text: Share this article Share He uploaded the video, which has been viewed more than 250,000 times, on Youtube with the heading: 'Look what I just saw in Nottingham city centre... wait for it.' Some social media users suggested it was 'cruel' to carry the cat around in the rucksack. The unusual backpack had air holes cut out at the bottom to allow the cat to breathe One person wrote: 'This is an absolute horror to have witnessed. Imagine being that poor cat.' However, others noted that it appeared that the rucksack had been especially designed for cats. Some also commented that they had thought the futuristic looking rucksack was a washing machine at first. Share or comment on this article Most watched News videos
